This directory should contain the following items:

- idat/ directory
  contains raw illumina .idat files
  obtained from:  https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/query/acc.cgi?acc=GSE279509
  located under:  Supplementary file > GSE279509_RAW.tar > (http)
  exact address:  https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/download/?acc=GSE279509&format=file

- GSE279509.txt file
  contains meta information about samples
  obtained from:  https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/query/acc.cgi?acc=GSE279509
  located under:  Scope: Samples > Format: SOFT > Amount: Brief > GO
  exact address:  https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/query/acc.cgi?acc=GSE279509&targ=gsm&form=text&view=brief

- EPIC.hg38.mask.tsv file
  contains masking information for illumina array probes
  obtained from:  https://zwdzwd.github.io/InfiniumAnnotation
  located under:  Mask information > Previous Versions > EPIC
  exact address:  https://github.com/zhou-lab/InfiniumAnnotationV1/raw/main/Anno/EPIC/archive/202209/EPIC.hg38.mask.tsv.gz
